            <li>Watch any class any time on our streaming player</li>
            <li>Totally ad-free</li>
            <li>Special download rate $2.99</li>
          </ul>
          <%= link_to_function( image_tag('getstarted_unlimited_showdetails.png', :alt => 'Show Details', :class => 'getstarted_details'), "togglePopup(this, 'unlimited')", {:class => 'toggle_link', :title => "Show Details"}) -%>
          <div class="popup" style="display: none;">
            <div>
              <p>The Unlimited Membership was designed for those who make yoga practice a part of everyday life. Subscribers enjoy ad-free streaming access to the entire Yoga Today library of over 200 one-hour classes</p>
              <p>As an Unlimited Member, you can practice with Adi, Neesha, and Sarah, as often as you like using our full-screen, streaming player. For subscribers, the Yoga Queue is especially useful. As you search the library, add classes to your Queue to build your own lineup of one-hour workouts.</p>
              <p>Subscribe at $9.99/month or save 25% when you opt for a full year of Yoga Today at $89.95. Subscribers enjoy a discounted download rate of only $2.99 per class.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <%= link_to image_tag('button_getstarted_unlimited.png', :alt => 'Sign Up'), subscription_users_path(:membership => '12'), :class => 'getstarted_button', :title => 'Subscribe to Yoga Today' %>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</div>


<script type="text/javascript">
  function togglePopup(link_element, option) {
    // Update the button first
    var current_image = jQuery(link_element).children()[0];
    var current_image_path = current_image.src.split('/');
    var current_image_name = current_image_path[current_image_path.length-1];

    if (current_image_name == 'getstarted_'+ option +'_showdetails.png') {
      current_image.src = '/images/getstarted_'+ option +'_hidedetails.png';
    } else if (current_image_name == 'getstarted_'+ option +'_hidedetails.png') {
      current_image.src = '/images/getstarted_'+ option +'_showdetails.png';
    } else {
      current_image.src = '/images/getstarted_'+ option +'_hidedetails.png';
    }
    // Toggle the display of the popup itself
    jQuery(link_element).parent().children('.popup').toggle();

  }

  function selectAmbassador() {
    window.location = "/users/select_ambassador?ambassador_name=" + jQuery("#x_ambassador_name").val();
  }

  function returning_user_signup() {
    path = "<%= current_user ? billing_user_path(current_user) : new_session_path %>";
    window.location = path + "?membership=" + jQuery("input[name=membership]:checked").val();
  }
</script>

